libvaht
------------------------------------------
This is an early version of libvaht, a Mohawk archive and resource reader.
Mohawk is used as the engine of Riven, versions of Myst, and some other games.
Vaht is d'ni for five, as Riven is Gehn's fifth age.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libpng16-1.6.42-1
  libvaht-devel-0.3+git20160107-1bl2
  libvaht0-0.3+git20160107-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libpng-devel-1.6.42-1
  libtool-2.5.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/agrif/libvaht

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/agrif/libvaht.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libvaht-0.3+git20160107-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libvaht-0.3+git20160107-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libvaht-0.3+git20160107-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libvaht-0.3+git20160107-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libvaht0-0.3+git20160107-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libvaht-devel-0.3+git20160107-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libvaht)
  /usr/bin/vahttool.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libvaht.README
  /usr/share/doc/libvaht/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libvaht/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libvaht/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libvaht/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libvaht/README

(libvaht0)
  /usr/bin/cygvaht-0.dll

(libvaht-devel)
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_archive.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_blst.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_bmp.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_card.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_hspt.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_mov.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_name.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_plst.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_resource.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_rmap.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_script.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_slst.h
  /usr/include/vaht/vaht_wav.h
  /usr/lib/libvaht.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libvaht.pc

